quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  39,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  39,1,iss kitaab ka nuzool Allah zabardast aur Dana ki taraf se hai
  39,2,"( aeMuhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam) yeh kitaab hum ne tumhari taraf brhq nazil ki hai, lehaza tum Allah hi ki bandagi karo deen ko usi ke liye khalis karte hue"
  39,3,"khabardaar, deen khalis Allah ka haq hai rahay woh log jinhon ne uss ke siwa dosray sarparast bana rakhay hain ( aur apne iss feal ki tojeeh yeh karte hain ke ) hum to unn ki ibadat sirf is liye karte hain ke woh Allah taq hamari rasai kara den, Allah yaqeenan unn ke darmain unn tamam baton ka faisla kar day ga jin mein woh ikhtilaaf kar rahay hain Allah kisi aisay shakhs ko hadaayat nahi deta jo jhoota aur munkir haq ho"
  39,4,"agar Allah kisi ko beta banana chahta to apni makhlooq mein se jis ko chahta bargzida kar laita, pak hai woh is se ( ke koi uss ka beta ho ), woh Allah hai akela aur sab par ghalib"
  39,5,"is ne asmano aur zameen ko brhq peda kya hai wohi din par raat aur raat par din ko liptahai usi ne Sooraj aur chaand ko is terhan maskhar kar rakha hai ke har aik aik waqt muqarrar taq chalay ja raha hai jaan rakho, woh zabardast hai aur dar guzar karne wala hai"
  39,6,"usi ne tum ko aik jaan se peda kya, phir wohi hai jis ne uss jaan se is ka jora banaya aur isi ne tumahray liye maweshion mein se aath nar o madah peda kiye woh tumhari maaon ke piton mein teen teen tareek pardon ke andar tumhe aik ke baad aik shakal deta chala jata hai yahi Allah ( jis ke yeh kaam hain ) tumhara rab hai, badshahi isi ki hai, koi mabood is ke siwa nahi hai, phir tum kidhar se phira-ay ja rahay ho ?"
  39,7,"agar tum kufar karo to Allah tum se be niaz hai, lekin woh apne bundon ke liye kufar ko pasand nahi karta, aur agar tum shukar kar o to usay woh tumahray liye pasand karta hai koi boojh uthany wala kisi dosray ka boojh nah uthaye ga aakhir kaar tum sab ko apne rab ki taraf palatna hai, phir woh tumhe bta day ga ke tum kya karte rahay ho, woh to dilon ka haal taq jaanta hai"
  39,8,"ensaan par jab koi aafat aati hai to woh apne rab ki taraf rujoo kar ke ussay pukaarta hai phir jab is ka rab usay apni Nemat se Nawaz deta hai to woh uss museebat ko bhool jata hai jis par woh pehlay pukaar raha tha aur dosaron ko Allah ka humsartehraتا hai taakay uss ki raah se gumraah kere ( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) uss se kaho ke thoray din apne kufar se lutaf utha le, yaqeenan to dozakh mein jaane wala hai"
  39,9,"( kya iss shakhs ki rawish behtar hai ya uss shakhs ki ) jo Mutee farmaan hai, raat ki gharion mein khara rehta aur sjday karta hai, akhirat se darta aur apne rab ki rehmat se umeed lagaata hai? inn se pucho, kya jan-nay walay aur nah jan-nay walay dono kabhi yaksaa ho satke hain? nasiyaat to aqal rakhnay walay hi qubool karte hain"
  39,10,"( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) kaho ke ae mere Bandoo jo imaan laaye ho, apne rab se daro jin logon ne iss duniya mein naik rawayya ikhtiyar kya hai un ke liye bhalai hai aur khuda ki zameen wasee hai, sabr karne walon ko to un ka ajar be hisaab diya jaye ga"
  39,11,"( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) inn se kaho, mujhe hukum diya gaya hai ke deen ko Allah ke liye khalis kar ke uss ki bandagi karoon"
  39,12,aur mujhe hukum diya gaya hai ke sab se pehlay mein khud muslim banon
  39,13,"kaho, agar mein apne rab ki nafarmani karoon to mujhe aik barray din ke azaab ka khauf hai"
  39,14,keh do ke mein to apne deen ko Allah ke liye khalis kar ke usi ki bandagi karoon ga
  39,15,"tum uss ke siwa jis jis ki bandagi karna chaho karte raho kaho, asal diwalyay to wohi hain jinhon ne qayamat ke roz apne aap ko aur apne ahal o Ayal ko ghatay mein daal diya khoob sun rakho, yahi khula dewala hai"
  39,16,"unn par aag ki chutriyan oopar se bhi chhai hon gi aur neechay se bhi yeh woh injaam hai jis se Allah apne bundon ko darata hai, pas ae mere Bandoo , mere ghazab se bachcho"
  39,17,bakhilaf is ke jin logon ne Taghoot ki bandagi se ijtinab kya aur Allah ki taraf rujoo kar liya unn ke liye khushkhabri hai pas ( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) basharat day do mere unn bundon ko
  39,18,jo baat ko ghhor se suntay hain aur is ke behtareen pehlu ki pairwi karte hain yeh woh log hain jin ko Allah ne hadaayat bakhsh hai aur yahi danishmand hain
  39,19,( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) uss shakhs ko kon bacha sakta hai jis par azaab ka faisla chaspan ho chuka ho? kya tum ussay bacha satke ho jo aag mein gir chuka ho ?
  39,20,"Albata jo log apne rab se dar kar rahay unn ke liye buland emiratein hain manzil par manzil bani hui, jin ke neechay nhrin beh rahi hon gi yeh Allah ka wada hai, Allah kabhi apne waday ki khilaaf warzi nahi karta"
  39,21,"kya tum nahi dekhte ke Allah ne aasman se pani barsaya, phir is ko soton aur chashmo aur daryaaon ki shakal mein zameen ke andar jari kya, phir is pani ke zareya se woh terhan terhan ki khityan nkalta hai jin ki kasmain mukhtalif hain, phir woh khityan pick kar sookh jati hain, phir tum dekhte ho ke woh zard par gayeen, phir aakhir kaar Allah unn ko bhus bana deta hai Dur haqeeqat iss mein aik sabaq hai aqal rakhnay walon ke liye"
  39,22,ab kya woh shakhs jis ka seenah Allah ne islam ke liye khol diya aur woh apne rab ki taraf se aik roshni par chal raha hai ( uss shakhs ki terhan ho sakta hai jis ne inn baton se koi sabaq nah liya? ) tabahi hai unn logon ke liye jin ke dil Allah ki nasiyaat se aur ziyada sakht ho gay woh khuli gumraahi mein parre hue hain
  39,23,"Allah ne behtareen kalaam utaara hai, aik aisi kitaab jis ke tamam ajzaa hum rang hain aur jis mein baar baar mazameen duhraey gay hain ussay sun kar unn logon ke rongte kharray ho jatay hain jo apne rab se darny walay hain, aur phir un ke jism aur un ke dil naram ho kar Allah ke zikar ki taraf Raghib ho jatay hain yeh Allah ki hadaayat hai jis se woh raah raast par le aata hai jisay chahta hai aur jisay Allah hi hadaayat nah day is ke liye phir koi haadi nahi hai"
  39,24,ab uss shakhs ki bad haali ka tum kya andaza kar satke ho jo qayamat ke roz azaab ki sakht maar apne mun par le ga? aisay zaalmon se to keh diya jaye ga ke ab chako maza uss kamaai ka jo tum karte rahay thay
  39,25,inn se pehlay bhi bohat se log isi terhan jhutla chuke hain aakhir unn par azaab aisay rukh se aaya jidhar un ka khayaal bhi nah ja sakta tha
  39,26,"phir Allah ne un ko duniya hi ki zindagi mein ruswai ka maza chakhaaya, aur akhirat ka azaab to is se shadeed tar hai, kash yeh log jantay"
  39,27,hum ne iss quran mein logon ko terhan terhan ki misalein di hain ke yeh hosh mein ayen
  39,28,"aisa quran jo arabi zabaan mein hai, jis mein koi theerh nahi hai, taakay yeh buray injaam se bachchen"
  39,29,"Allah aik misaal deta haishakhs to woh hai jis ki malkiat mein bohat se kaj Khalq aaqa shareek hain jo usay apni apni taraf khinchte hain aur dosra shakhs poora ka poora aik hi aaqa ka ghulam hai kya un dono ka haal yaksaa ho sktahe? Alhamdo Lillaha, magar aksar log nadani mein parre hue hain"
  39,30,( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) tumhe bhi marna hai aur inn logon ko bhi marna hai
  39,31,aakhir kaar qayamat ke roz tum sab apne rab ke huzoor apna apna muqadma paish karo ge
  39,32,phir uss shakhs se bara zalim aur kon ho ga jis ne Allah par jhoot baandha aur jab sachaai is ke samnay aayi to ussay jhutla diya kya aisay kafiroon ke liye jahannum mein koi thikana nahi hai ?
  39,33,"aur jo shakhs sachaai le kar aaya aur jinhon ne is ko sach maana, wohi azaab se bachney walay hain"
  39,34,inhen apne rab ke haan woh sab kuch miley ga jis ki woh khwahish karen ge yeh hai neki karne walon ki jaza
  39,35,taakay jo bad tareen aamaal unhon ne kiye thay inhen Allah un ke hisaab se saqt kar day aur jo behtareen aamaal woh karte rahay unn ke lehaaz se unn ko ajar ataa farmaiye
  39,36,( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) kya Allah apne bande ke liye kaafi nahi hai? yeh log uss ke siwa dosaron se tum ko darate hain halaank Allah jisay gumraahi mein daal day ussay koi rasta dikhaane wala nahi
  39,37,"aur jisay woh hadaayat day ussay bhataknay wala bhi koi nahi, kya Allah zabardast aur intiqam lainay wala nahi hai ?"
  39,38,"inn logon se agar tum pucho ke zameen aur asmano ko kis ne peda kya hai to yeh khud kahin ge ke Allah ne inn se kaho, jab haqeeqat yeh hai to tumhara kya khayaal hai ke agar Allah mujhe koi nuqsaan pahunchana chahay to kya tumhari yeh dewyan, jinhein tum Allah ko chore kar pkarte ho, mujhe uss ke p_hnchaye hue nuqsaan se bacha len gi? ya Allah mujh par meharbani karna chahay to kya yeh is ki rehmat ko rok saken gi? bas un se keh do ke mere liye Allah hi kaafi hai, bharosa karne walay usi par bharosa karte hain"
  39,39,"un se saaf kaho ke"" ae meri qoum ke logo, tum apni jagah apna kaam kiye jao, mein apna kaam karta rahon ga, anqareeb tumhe maloom ho jaye ga"
  39,40,"ke kis par ruswa kin azaab aata hai aur kisay woh saza millti hai jo kabhi talnay wali nahi """
  39,41,"( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) hum ne sab insanon ke liye yeh kitaab brhq tum par nazil kar di hai ab jo seedha rasta ikhtiyar kere ga apne liye kere ga aur jo bhatkay ga uss ke bhatakne ka wabaal usi par hoga, tum unn ke zimma daar nahi ho"
  39,42,"woh Allah hi hai jo mout ke waqt roohein qabz karta hai aur jo abhi nahi mra hai uss ki rooh neend mein qabz kar laita hai, phir jis par woh mout ka faisla nafiz karta hai ussay rok laita hai aur dosaron ki roohein aik waqt muqarrar ke liye wapas bhaij deta hai iss mein barri nishanain hain unn logon ke liye jo ghhor o fikar karne walay hain"
  39,43,"kya uss khuda ko chore kar inn logon ne dosaron ko Shafi bana rakha hai? un se kaho, kya woh Shafaat karen ge khuwa unn ke ikhtiyar mein kuch nah ho aur woh samajte bhi nah hon ?"
  39,44,"kaho, Shafaat saari ki saari Allah ke ikhtiyar mein hai asmano aur zameen ki badshahi ka wohi maalik hai phir usi ki taraf tum pulta-ay jaane walay ho"
  39,45,"jab akailey Allah ka zikar kya jata hai to akhirat par imaan nah rakhnay walon ke dil krhhne lagtay hain, aur jab uss ke siwa dosaron ka zikar hota hai to yakayak woh khusi se khil uthte hain"
  39,46,"kaho, khudaaya! asmano aur zameen ke peda karne walay, haazir o gayab ke jan-nay walay, to hi apne bundon ke darmain uss cheez ka faisla kere ga jis mein woh ikhtilaaf karte rahay hain"
  39,47,"agar inn zaalmon ke paas zameen ki saari doulat bhi ho, aur itni hi aur bhi, to yeh roz qayamat ke buray azaab se bachney ke liye sab kuch فدیے mein dainay ke liye tayyar ho jayen ge wahan Allah ki taraf se un ke samnay woh kuch aeye ga jis ka unhon ne kabhi andaza hi nahi kya hai"
  39,48,wahan apni kamaai ke saaray buray nataij un par khil jayen ge aur wohi cheez un par musallat ho jaye gi jis ka yeh mazaq uratay rahay hain
  39,49,"yahi ensaan jab zara si museebat isay chhoo jati hai to hamein pukaarta hai, aur jab hum usay apni taraf se Nemat day kar aphaar dete hain to kehta hai ke yeh to mujhe ilm ki bana par diya gaya hai! nahi, balkay yeh azmaish hai, magar un mein se aksar log jantay nahi hain"
  39,50,"yahi baat un se pehlay guzray hue log bhi keh chuke hain, magar jo kuch woh kamate thay woh un ke kisi kaam nah aaya"
  39,51,"phir apni kamaai ke buray nataij unhon ne bhugtey, aur inn logon mein se bhi jo zalim hain woh anqareeb apni kamaai ke buray nataij bhgtin ge, yeh hamein aajiz kar dainay walay nahi hain"
  39,52,aur kya inhen maloom nahi hai ke Allah jis ka chahta hai rizaq kushadah kar deta hai aur jis ka chahta hai tang kar deta hai? is mein nishanain hain unn logon ke liye jo imaan laatay hain
  39,53,"( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) keh do ke ae mere Bandoo , jinhon ne apni jaanun par zayad-ti ki hai, Allah ki rehmat se mayoos nah ho jao, yaqeenan Allah saaray gunah maaf kar deta hai, woh to ghafoor o Raheem hai"
  39,54,palat aao apne rab ki taraf aur Mutee ban jao uss ke qabal iss ke ke tum par azaab aa jaye aur phir kahin se tumhe madad nah mil sakay
  39,55,"aur pairwi ikhtiyar kar lau apne rab ki bhaije hui kitaab ke behtareen pehlu ki, qabal iss ke ke tum par achanak azaab aeye aur tum ko khabar bhi nah ho"
  39,56,"kahin aisa nah ho ke baad mein koi shakhs kahe"" afsos meri uss taqseer par jo mein Allah ki janab mein karta raha, balkay mein to ulta mazaq urane walon mein shaamil tha """
  39,57,"ya kahe"" kash Allah ne mujhe hadaayat bakhsh hoti to mein bhi Muttaqiyun mein se hota """
  39,58,"ya azaab dekh kar kahe"" kash mujhe aik mauqa aur mil jaye aur mein bhi naik amal karne walon mein shaamil ho jaoon """
  39,59,"( aur uss waqt usay yeh jawab miley ke )"" kyun nahi, meri ayaat tairay paas aa chuki theen, phir to ne inhen jhtlaya aur taqqabur kya aur to kafiroon mein se tha """
  39,60,aaj jin logon ne khuda par jhoot bandhay hain qayamat ke roz tum dekho ge ke un ke mun kalay hon ge kya jahannum mein mtkbron ke liye kaafi jagah nahi hai ?
  39,61,"is ke bar aks jin logon ne yahan taqwa kya hai un ke asbaab kamyabi ki wajah se Allah un ko nijaat day ga, un ko nah koi gznd puhanche ga aur nah woh ghamgeen hon ge"
  39,62,Allah har cheez ka khaaliq hai aur wohi har cheez par nigehbaan hai
  39,63,zameen aur asmano ke khazanon ki knjyan usi ke paas hain aur jo log Allah ki ayaat se kufar karte hain wohi ghatay mein rehne walay hain
  39,64,"( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) inn se kaho"" phir kya ae جاہلو, tum Allah ke siwa kisi aur ki bandagi karne ke liye mujh se kehte ho? """
  39,65,( yeh baat tumhe un se saaf keh dainee chahiye kyunkay ) tumhari taraf aur tum se pehlay guzray hue tamam anbia ki taraf yeh wahi bhaije ja chuki hai ke agar tum ne shirk kya to tumhara amal zaya ho jaye ga aur tum khasaray mein raho ge
  39,66,lehaza ( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) tum bas Allah hi ki bandagi karo aur shukar guzaar bundon mein se ho jao
  39,67,inn logon ne Allah ki qader hi nah ki jaissa ke is ki qader karne ka haq hai ( is ki qudrat kamila ka haal to yeh hai ke ) qayamat ke roz poori zameen uss ki muthi mein ho gi aur aasman is ke dast raast mein liptay hue hon ge pak aur balatar hai woh is shirk se jo yeh log karte hain
  39,68,aur uss roz sor phonka jaye ga aur woh sab mar kar gir jayen ge jo asmano aur zameen mein hain siwaye unn ke jinhein Allah zindah rakhna chahay phir aik dosra sor phonka jaye ga aur yakayak sab ke sab uth kar dekhnay lagen ge
  39,69,"zameen apne rab ke noor se chamak utthay gi, kitaab aamaal laa kar rakh di jaye gi, anbia aur tamam gawah haazir kar diye jayen ge, logon ke darmain theek theek haq ke sath faisla kar diya jaye ga aur unn par koi zulm nah hoga"
  39,70,aur har mutnaqas ko jo kuch bhi uss ne amal kya tha uss ka poora poora badla day diya jaye ga log jo kuch bhi karte hain Allah is ko khoob jaanta hai
  39,71,"( iss faisla ke baad ) woh log jinhon ne kufar kya tha jahannum ki taraf giroh Dur giroh hankay jayen ge, yahan taq ke jab woh wahan pohnchain ge to is ke darwazay khole jayen ge aur uss ke karnde un se kahin ge"" kya tumahray paas tumahray apne logon mein se aisay rasool nahi aeye thay, jinhon ne tum ko tumahray rab ki ayaat sunai hon aur tumhe is baat se daraya ho ke aik waqt tumhe yeh din bhi dekhna hoga ?"" woh jawab den ge"" haan, aeye thay, magar azaab ka faisla kafiroon par chipak gaya """
  39,72,"kaha jaye ga, daakhil ho jao jahannum ke darwazon mein, yahan ab tumhe hamesha rehna hai, bara hi bura thikana hai yeh mtkbron ke liye"
  39,73,"aur jo log apne rab ki nafarmani se parhaiz karte thay inhen giroh Dur giroh jannat ki taraf le jaya jaye ga yahan taq ke jab woh wahan pohnchain ge, aur is ke darwazay pehlay hi khole ja chuke hon ge, to uss ke muntazmeen un se kahin ge ke"" salam ho tum par, bohat achay rahay, daakhil ho jao is mein hamesha ke liye """
  39,74,"aur woh kahin ge"" shukar hai uss khuda ka jis ne hamaray sath apna wada sach kar dekhaya aur hum ko zameen ka waris bana diya, ab hum jannat mein jahan chahain apni jagah bana satke hain"" pas behtareen ajar hai amal karne walon ke liye"
  39,75,"aur tum dekho ge ke farishtay arsh ke gird halqa banaye hue apne rab ki hamd aur tasbeeh kar rahay hon ge, aur logon ke darmain theek theek haq ke sath faisla chuka diya jaye ga, aur pukaar diya jaye ga ke hamd hai Allah Rab alaalmin ke liye"
